{
  "texts": [
    "The ethical consideration of our research in developing the INJECAGENT benchmark primarily stems from the dual-use nature of disclosed vulnerabilities.",
    "By revealing these vulnerabilities, our goal is to preemptively strengthen the NLP community against potential exploits, thereby promoting a culture of enhanced security and resilience.",
    "Although we acknowledge that sharing information about these weaknesses might lead to their misuse, we argue that it is crucial to be aware of them in order to safeguard against such threats.",
    "Additionally, we have disclosed our findings to OpenAI and Anthropic to ensure they are aware of the vulnerabilities.",
    "Therefore, we believe that our paper is in alignment with ethical principles."
  ]
}